* Nkaasiveliwe nthowa nawi naanachuna atiithi ahu .
Xaxaxa okhwa wootutuxa , muchu okhweliwe wiiliwiili onnuupuwela , ‘ akhweya ela hiyaahaala weereya waakhanle wi koopaka ela naari ele . ’
Wakhala wi munnawana ni mukhalelo ntoko wiisoona okhalano nthowa ni wiikhupanyerya , ti yaphaama ohuupuwela moonelo yoowo .
Moohiyana , muloce ni nthamwene yoowo onahaala woowiriyanaani ni woohakararyaani , wi moonelo ntoko yoowo ti wawunlaana wa achu ancipale akhweliwe .
Piipiliya onnaleela : “ Nthamwene onamukhwela nthamwene’awe mahiku othene , onnakhala munnawe , elukuluku y’epahu . ” — Masiposipo 17 : 17 .
Nthamwene aphaama a muchu okhweliwe onaphwaneleiye okhalano ti Mpatuxa ahu , Yehova Muluku .
Mmiinele murima anyu wa yoowo mu nivekelo nthowa nawi “ ti yowo onokhapelelani . ”
( 1 Pedro 5 : 7 ) Opwaha yeeyo , owo onnalaiherya wi yaawo aneera hiiha , moonelo ni muupuwelo aya inamukhapeleliwa ni “ muretxele wa Muluku , onapwaha miruku sothene . ”
( Filipi 4 : 6 , 7 ) Nave tho , mweemererye wi Muluku ookhaviheryeeni openuwa moorweela wa Masu awe oohakararya , Piipiliya .
Wuupuwelela soorepa iho enahaala okhala yookhaviherya xaxaxa ohiyu vaavaa munakhalaanyu meekhinyu nave muhinaweryaanyu orupa . — Isaiya 57 : 15 .
Hiihaanoru , mulopwana a iyaakha 40 , oniichaniwa Jack , oomuyeleela mwaariye nthowa na ereca ya Kanser .
Owo onnathariha : “ Vaavaa kinavekelaaka wa Yehova , nkinoona omeekha .
Wiiliwiili kinnavinya ohiyu eriyari , nave nkinawerya okookela orupa .
Kimanle waalakhanya ni wuupuwelela soorepa soohakararya ni omiinela murima wa Yehova , kinnamaaliheya ni murecele onarweela wirimu , weerihaka wi murima ni muupuwelo aka wiichuuwe nave kiwerye orupa . ”
Mwali oniichaniwa Vanesa ohaayeleela amannya nthowa na ereca .
Owo tho onnoona ikuru sa nivekelo .
Owo onnaloca : “ Mu ilukuluku saka sookacamiha , pahiru kaaphwanela wiichana nsina na Muluku nave kaanakokhora kinnlaka .
Yehova aanawiriyana mavekelo aka nave wiiliwiili aanakivaha ikuru kaachunaaka . ”
