Waahakararya Yaale Ananla Apwanne montoko okhala ookhulumuwa nthowa na muchu omuyeleenle oosiveliwa awe ?
Ikwaha ikina nnanwerya ohisuwela echu yooloca naari yaweera — mwawiihiiha haniwerya oloca echu naari opaka echu vyakala .
Nyenya sookhalawo ichu ikina nnaphwanelaahu okhaviherya .
Ikwaha soothene , echu enachuneya ori ophiya wanyu vamoha ni masu anyu ntoko “ Kinnathanana tho . ”
Mu sookhovelela sincipale , omukhupaarela mukhalelo waphaama wa wooniherya opwacha .
Wakhala wi muchu okhweliwe onachuna oloca , mmuwiriyane phaama .
Opwaha soothene , opaka echu ntakhara emusi ekhweliwe , ntoko waapeya yoolya , waakhapelela anamwane , naari okhaviherya marehereryo a ovitha muruchu echu yookhweleya .
Miteko ntoko seiyo sinanwerya okhala sa mphurelo opwaha masu aphaama .
Mweelukuluku aya , munanwerya oloca sa muchu okhwile , akhweya mulocaka makhalelo aphaama naari ichu soohakalaliha aapankeiye .
Ovaneela ntoko yoola onanwerya omuhakalaliha muchu okhweliwe .
Ntoko yootakiherya , Pam — yoowo omuyeleenle iyawe Lan , mu iyaakha thanu nammoha ivirale — onnaloca : “ Ikwaha ikina achu annakileela ichu saphaama Lan eereiye miyaano kahaasuwelaaka , nave eyo yaanakihakalaliha . ”
Moohiciha , otholathola weeriweno wohooniherya wi achu ancipale akhweliwe yaakhenle nikhaviheryo voopaceryani , nyenya soochuna saya moohilekela saacuwaliwa ni asinthamwene nthowa na ooweiwa ni miteko saya .
Mwawiihiiha , mwiilipixerye oloca ni nthamwene okhweliwe moohihiyererya .
* Achu ancipale akhweliwe annathamalela vancipale ekari yeela enaakhaviherya woopowa mmukhalelo aya woothanana .
Muthokororye yaweereya ya Kaori , mwali o Xapau yoowo aayelenle amanya , voocharela aamuyeleela murokora awe awunnuwelavo ivinrevo miyeeri 15 .
Moohakalaliha aahaakhela nikhaviheryo moohihiyererya orweela wa asinthamwene oororomeleya .
Mmoha iichaniwa Ritsuko tawunnuwelavo ompwaha Kaori , aahiivaha wi akhale nthamwene awe — waakhala wi yaari amama awe .
Kaori onnaloca : “ Wi kiloce eparipari miyaano nkaari oohakalala ni yeeyo .
Nkaachuna wi muchu apake nikupa na amama aka , nave kuupuwela wi muchu mukina haahaala owerya .
Nyenya , nthowa na Mama Ritsuko okikhaliha wawe phaama , miyaano kaakhala nthamwene awe .
Isuma soothene , naanaya vamoha mmuteko wa olaleerya ni oya mmithukumanoni vamoha .
Owo aanakiwopa wi kanwurye chaaya ni yene , anakiruheela yoolya , ni okirepela ikaarata mu ilukuluku sincipale .
Mukhalelo waphaama wa Mama Ritsuko waakivolowela mwakuru . ”
Sooviravo iyaakha khumi napiili amannya Kaori ekhwili , nave olelo owo ni iyawe alaleeryi a elukuluku yoothene .
Kaori onnaloca : “ Mama Ritsuko onnatitelela okipwacha .
Kaachikelaka nipuro kiyariwaakawo , wiiliwiili kinnamuxekurya nave kinnapuha onthamwene awe woolipiha . ”
Yootakiherya ekina ya muchu yoowo aakhenle nikhaviheryo moohihiyererya ti Poli yoowo ori Namoona a Yehova o Xipre .
Poli aakhalano iyawe eepewe , Sozos , yoowo ovanhe yootakiherya yaphaama ntoko mukukhula Eekiristu , moorweela wa owopa ikwaasuni ni anaamukhwele wi yalye owannyawe .
( Tiyako 1 : 27 ) Moothananiha , arino iyaakha 53 , Sozos aakhwa ni ereca ya ocoopare .
Weiwo yaapacerya othukumana ni muloko wa Anamoona a Yehova .
Poli onnuupuwela . “ Asinthamwene a muloko aka muvyaani hiyaasuwenle echu vooloca sa yaweereya ahu ni mikhalelo sahu sookacamiha .
Nyenya eyo hiyaweerinhe omaala onaacamela ni onihakararya ni masu aya eepewe ni nikhaviheryo noophara muteko .
Nikhaviheryo nla naari na esisapo mu elukuluku mwanaka aachuneiye atiithi awe !
Yaale yaahoolela muloko yaahooniherya nchuno ntokweene wa Taniyeli .
Mmoha aapaka marehereryo a omvoliiherya Taniyeli mmathateloni mwaya ni asinthamwene ophitaanyerya vaavaa yaayaaya omvonya mphirya . ”
Oopiili , maai ni mwaana anneerano phaama olelo .
Mweeparipari , aakhalavo makhalelo mancipale nnaphwanelaahu ovaha nikhaviheryo ni nihakararyo wa yaale ananla .
Piipiliya tho onnanihakararya moorweela wa onivaha ewehereryo ya omwaahiyu .
[ Nsu na vathi ] Akina annarepela nihiku muchu okhwileiye wi yuupuweleleke wi evaha nihakararyo wakhala woochuneya — va nihiku nenlo naari ohoolo waya .
Achu Ookhwa Anamukhala Wanaawiili ! Akhweya munnamuupuwela Kail , olociwe woopaceryani wa miyaha seiya , owo aanakhwa minikwa waakhanle wi onahaala omaliha osooseya wawe mmurima nthowa na iyawe okhwile .
Nyenya owo onnaweherya omoona Roperto wanawiili mu elapo evyaani elaiheryiwe ni Muluku .
Moonelo aka onalikana ni wa achu yaawo yaayeleenle achu yaasivelaaya nyenya ahirino ewehereryo ya okhalano wanawiili oosiveliwa aya .
Moohilekela , Muluku onahaala weerano yeeyo — ntakhara Yuupu ni akina oohaalakhanyeya — vaavaa elapo ela enahaalaaya otatuxiwa okhala parataiso .
( Luka 23 : 42 , 43 ) Saweriwa T’arummwa onnooniherya wi “ ananvinya mokhwani . ”
Yesu tho onroromeliha ariki : “ Muhitikhine ni yela : enamurwa elukuluku atxhu othene ari mmahiyeni aneraya yiwe nsu nawe nave anamukhumamo . ”
Yuupu onnawehererya okhalano mwiili woolipa “ ntoko ole wa mmiravo . ”
( Yobi 33 : 24 , 25 ) Emohamoha enahaala weereya ni oothene yaale anathamalela ikharari sa Muluku sa ovinya mookhwani ntakhara okumi veelaponi yavathi .
