MWAHA WA EKAAPA | NTAKHARA HEENI YESU AAHOOXEYA NAVE AKHWA ?
Mu elimwi ya 33 E.K . , Yesu o Kaisareya aahiiphiwa .
Owo aahootheryiwa ntoko mulipa oohuweliha , nave aakhomeliwa vamwirini .
Nyenya Muluku aamukookiherya okumi , nave mahiku 40 ohoolo waya , Yesu aakookela wirimu .
Yaweereya ela yootikhiniha ennanuupuxerya Michaka misese sa Soorempwa Seekiriki , iniichaniwa Nlakano na Hiihaano .
( 1 Korinto 15 : 14 ) Mmukhalelo mukina , waakhanle wi ichu seiye soheereya , wookhalavo omwaahiyu wootikhiniha wa achu , yoowo munahaalaanyu ophura .
Mwawiihiiha , apwanne saweereya seiya sa Michaka ti seeparipari naari hooye ?
YEEYO SAWEEREYA INOONIHERYAAYA Moohiyana ni ithale , ichu seiyo anamarepa a Michaka arempaaya ti seeparipari .
Ntoko yootakiherya , aarepa masina a mapuro eeparipari , mancipale a yaawo anaxekuryiwa olelo .
Ahaaloca achu yaawo okhala waya oniiwanana ni miyaha sa elapo . — Luka 3 : 1 , 2 , 23 .
Yesu onnalociwa ni anamarepa a nsana noopacerya ni nanawiili .
* Okhwa wawe ntoko onatharihiwaaya mu Michaka onniiwanana ni meerelo a wiipha a Aroma a elukuluku yeele .
Opwaha yeeyo saweereya soothene ti seeparipari ophiyerya wi sinnaloca soohesa sa oohuserya a Yesu .
( Mateu 26 : 56 ; Luka 22 : 24 - 26 ; Yohani 18 : 10 , 11 ) Saweereya seiya soothene sinnooniherya wi anamarepa a Michaka yaari oororomeleya mwa yeeyo arempaaya vooloca sa Yesu .
HANKA VOOLOCA SA OVINYA WA YESU ?
Naamwi yeemereryiwaka wi Yesu aakhala nave akhwa , akina annakhwa minikwa sa ovinya wawe .
( Luka 24 : 11 ) Vaavaa oohuserya yaamonnaaya Yesu mu ilukuluku soohiyana hiyana , minikwa saahaamalela .
Yaweereya emoha , yeeren’ye variyari va anamoona 500 . — 1 Korinto 15 : 6 .
Naamwi yoopopihiwa ni okhwa , oohuserya moolipa murima yaalaleerya ovinya wa Yesu wa oothene — ophiyerya wa yaawo yaamwiiphale owo .
( Saweriwa T’arummwa 4 : 1 - 3 , 10 , 19 , 20 ; 5 : 27 - 32 ) Apwanne oohuserya ancipale yaahaala okhala oolipa murima esuwelaka wi Yesu havinnye mookhwani ?
Mweeparipari , ovinya mookhwani wa Yesu waakhaviherya waaceereryeya wa Muloko Weekiristu khalai , ni hiihaano .
Saweereya sa Michaka vooloca sa okhwa ni ovinya wa Yesu sinnavaha onamoona weeparipari .
Waalakhanya seiyo mwawiichaalela sinahaala woolekechaani wi saweereya seiya chiryene soheereya .
Olekecheya wanyu onanwerya woolipihaani moorweela wa wiiwexexa ntakhara heeni iho soheereya .
[ Nsu na vathi ] Tasitu , aayariwe mu 55 E.K . , oorepa wi “ Kiristu , yoowo nsina na [ Akiristu ] nnarweelaayavo , aahooxeya vancipale variyari va olamulelo wa Tiperio ni muthoriha Pontio Pilato . ”
Yesu tho onnalociwa ni Suetoniu a ( nsana noopacerya ) ; Mulipa a miyaha a Ayuuta Yoosefe a ( nsana noopacerya ) ; ni Pliny mulamuleli Mmiravo o Pitiiniya ( waacamela nsana nanawiili ) . [ Ekaaxa va epaaxina 4 ]
( 1 Pedro 1 : 24 , 25 ) Nihiweherye wi tho amwiicani ancipale a Yesu yaahaala orepa echu vyakala yaahaala waakhaviherya achu omweemererya ni omuroromela Yesu .
Vooloca sa ovinya wa Yesu , Petro mmoha a oohuserya , oothariha : “ Muluku ònvinyiha mokhwani nihiku naneraru naya , ni àhera wi isoneihe , ohikhanle wa atxhu othene , nto wa anamona Muluku athanlileiye wopatxeryani , hiyo nlyile ni niwunrye ni yowo , avinnyeiye mokhwani . ”
Muchaka wa Mateu onnanleela wi amwiicani a ikerexa yiiwalaaya vooloca sa ovinya wa Yesu , awo yaaheererya omaaliha michaka vooloca sa ovinya wa Yesu . — Mateu 28 : 11 - 15 .
Apwanne eyo enooniherya wi Yesu aachuna wi ovinya wawe mookhwani ohisuweliwe ?
Hooye , woona wi Petro aaloca : “ Owo ònruma walalerya atxhu ni òlokoha wi Muluku òmwera Yesu muthoriha a akumi ni a atxhu òkhwa . ”
