Apwanne Muluku onnapaka echu wi arehererye mukhalelo yoola ?
Maakhulo a Mpiipiliyani toohakalaliha , nave mwemmo wookhalamo otharihiwa wookwakwaleya ntakhara heeni Yesu aahooxeya nave akhwa .
TIHEENI ENANANRE ? Icima raru soopacerya sa liivuru a Mpiipiliyani Maphatxuwelo onnaleela wi woopaceryani Muluku ahaakumve ompaka mutheli oopacerya Aatamu ni Haava , aatikitherya ekumi yoohimala nave aaloca yeeyo yaahaalaaya weera wi ekhaleno .
Voocharela saweereya sinnaloca mukhalelo awo ahensaaya omwiiwelela Muluku ni oyeleela ewehereryo yeela .
Saweereya sinalociwa mookhweya — ophiyerya wi akina annakuvela okhooca ntoko soororomela satheru .
Nyenya Maphatxuwelo , hiiha ntoko Michaka sinnavaha sawooniherya sincipale opacerya wa saweereya sa miyaha .
Teevi eri yookhumelela ya ohiiwelela wa Aatamu ?
Piipiliya onnaakhula mmukhalelo ola : “ Vano ntoko wa nthowa na mutxhu mmoha pahi [ Aatamu ] yòvolowa mwelaponi yotxheka , navetho ni yotxheka wòvolowa mwelaponi okhwa , hihatho okhwa wòhaphwanya atxhu othene , ntakhara atxhu othene àtxheka . ”
Hiiha owo ooyeleela ewehereryo ya okumi woohimala nave ookhwa .
Nave nloko nawe , noorava mukhalelo awe woocheka .
Apwanne Muluku onnapaka echu wi arehererye mukhalelo yoola ?
YEEYO MULUKU ONEEREIYE Aai , Muluku oopaka marehereryo wi oopole , naari alive , yeeyo Aatamu oyeleelinheiye nloko nawe , ewehereryo ya okumi woohimala .
Piipiliya onnaloca mu Aroma 6 : 23 : “ Nlivelo na yotxheka ti okhwa . ”
Ela enataphulela wi okhwa yookhumelela ya yoocheka .
Moolikana , hiyaano ninnacheka nave ntoko yookhumelela ya yoocheka , ninnakhwa .
Nyenya nnayariwa oochekeeni tahi nthowa nahu .
Moosivela Muluku aamurumiha Mwanawe , Yesu , wi aakhwaniherye “ nlivelo na yotxheka ” wa hiyo .
Piipiliya onnathariha mmukhalelo ola : “ Vamohamoha , ntoko eryaya atxhu othene ekhala òtxheka wa nthowa na ohiwelela wa mutxhu mmoharu , hihatho wa nthowa wa wiwelela wa mutxhu mmoha atxhu othene annokololiwa ti Muluku . ”
Owo aakhuma wirimu , akhala muchu oophaameya * , nave akhwa wa nthowa nahu .
Ntoko yookhumelela , yooweryeya wa hiyaano weeriwa achu eekhaikhai vamiithoni va Muluku ni okhalano ewehereryo ya okumi woohimala .
Vano , ntakhara heeni waaryaaya woochuneya wi Yesu akhwe wi aakhwaniherye yeela ?
Apwanne hiwaari wookhweya wa Muluku Aikuru Soothene weeriha wi anamwane a Aatamu ekhaleno ekumi yoohimala ?
