Ntoko yootakiherya , apwanne aahaala okhala eekhaikhai mu olakelela wi variyari va nloko na Aatamu taani ahaala ophwanelela okhalano ekumi yoohimala ?
Ahaala okhwaaniherye yoolaiherya awe ?
Muluku , moorweela wa weerano ekhaikhai ni olapa moowetha ntakhara ovuluxiwa wahu ennaniroromeliha wi owo onahaala weeraka yeeyo eri yaphaama .
Moorweela wa okhwa wa Yesu , Muluku oohula ephiro ya ya ekumi yoohimala Mparataiso veelaponi yavathi .
Moone masu a Yesu anaphwanyeya va Yohani 3 : 16 : “ Muluku òtepa wakhwela atxhu a mwelaponi , ophiyerya onvaha Mwana awe mmoharu , wi mutxhu onamwemererya yowo , ahirimele , nto akhaleno ekumi yohimala . ”
Mwawiihiiha okhwa wa Yesu yawooniherya ohiya pahiru ya ekhaikhai ya Muluku , nyenya osivela otokotoko oreiyeno ntakhara achu .
Vano , ntakhara heeni Yesu aahooxeya nave akhwa mmukhalelo woohooxa onalociwa mu Michaka ?
Vaavaa eehiweiye nave iikhalelaru oororomeleya , Yesu aakhooca masu a Musaserya awi achu hiyaahaala okhalaka oororomeleya wa Muluku vaavaa anakumanaayano ni makacamiho .
( Yobi 2 : 4 , 5 ) Masu ala akhweya yaakumiherya mphurelo Satana amanle omuhuweliha Aatamu wi acheke .
