( 1 Korinto 15 : 45 ) Owo ahooniherya wi Aatamu tho aahaala omwiiwelela Muluku waakhanle wi oothanla weerano hiiha .
Moorweela wa ovilela ni soohooxa , Yesu oonihiyerya nooniheryo wi ncharihe .
( 1 Pedro 2 : 21 ) Muluku oomvaha phatamari Mwanawe oophaameya ni awiiwelela , morweela wa omvaha okumi woohikhwa wirimu . NYUWAANO MUNII MPHURE HAI
