KIYARIWE mu 1926 o Krooksville , Ohio , Estatu Unitu .
Apapa ni amama hiyaarino ekerexa , nyenya yaanileela hiyaano anamwane athanu nachaaru wi n’ye okerexa .

Mu elukuluku yeeyo , mwaacamani iichaniwa Margaret Walker , mmoha a Anamoona a Yehova , aapacerya waaxekurya amama nave aanaaleela vooloca sa Piipiliya .
Nyenya kaaheererya owiriyana yeeyo yaathokororya aya .
Mutheli owo amanle waaxekurya ikwaha sincipale , Margaret aakikoha , “ Woosuwela nsina na Muluku ? ”
Kaaheerano , nave kaasuwela wi nsina na Muluku ti Yehova .
Kaachimakela wa asinthamwene aka nave kaaloca , “ Mwaphiya owannyu ohiyu , mmuhule Piipiliya anyu va Salumu 83 : 18 wi moone nsina na Muluku . ”
Nyuwaano munamuloca wi kaapacerya olaleerya elukuluku yeele .
Kaamuhuserya Piipiliya nave kaapatisiwa mu 1941 .
Ohoolo waya , kaathanliwa wi keecihe yoohuserya ya liivuru ya muloko .
Kaanaaceenyerya amama aka ni asinnaka wi erwe , nave oothene yaapacerya owiriyana yoohuserya ya liivuru yeeyo keecihaaka .
Ikwaha ikina vaavaa amama yaayaaya omithukumano , apapa yaanaakookiherya owaani .
